  "description": "Oblique in its most transcendent state — sine wave, near-zero fold, almost no bounce click, long slow attack. The prism LFO (0.2 Hz) breathes the spectral color continuously. Only the 6-facet delay and phaser remain audible as the note swells into a luminous column of refracted light. Aether: above the surface, pure light.",
